###New call to make the test work
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/Invoices

###Get All line items
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/LineItems

###Get lineItems of specific invoice
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/Invoices/30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/lineItems

###Get lineItems of specific invoice with expand
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/Invoices/30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?$expand=lineItems

###Get all Vendors
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/Vendors


###Get all CostCenters
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/CostCenters


###Get all Invoice Statuses (CodeList)
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/InvoiceStatus


###OData Metadata — verify all entities are exposed
GET http://localhost:4004/invoice/$metadata

###Deep Insert - Create new invoice with line items in one call

POST http://localhost:4004/invoice/Invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005",
  "invoiceNumber": "INV-2024-001",
  "invoiceDate": "2024-01-15",
  "dueDate": "2024-02-14",
  "grossAmount": "40000",
  "currency": "INR",
  "notes": "Laptop and accessories for new joiners",
  "vendor_ID": "20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "costCenter_ID": "10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "status_code": "D",
  "lineItems": [
    {
      "ID": "40000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011",
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T06:02:16.431Z",
      "createdBy": "anonymous",
      "modifiedAt": "2026-05-20T06:02:16.431Z",
      "modifiedBy": "anonymous",
      "invoice_ID": "30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "positionNumber": 1,
      "description": "Dell Laptop 15 inch",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 60000,
      "amount": 120000
    },
    {
      "ID": "40000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000012",
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T06:02:16.431Z",
      "createdBy": "anonymous",
      "modifiedAt": "2026-05-20T06:02:16.431Z",
      "modifiedBy": "anonymous",
      "invoice_ID": "30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "positionNumber": 2,
      "description": "Laptop Bag",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 5000,
      "amount": 10000
    },
    {
      "ID": "40000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000013",
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T06:02:16.431Z",
      "createdBy": "anonymous",
      "modifiedAt": "2026-05-20T06:02:16.431Z",
      "modifiedBy": "anonymous",
      "invoice_ID": "30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "positionNumber": 3,
      "description": "Wireless Mouse and Keyboard",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 10000,
      "amount": 20000
    }
  ]
}

###Add new line item for existing invoice
POST http://localhost:4004/invoice/LineItems
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "invoice_ID": "30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "positionNumber": 5,
    "description": "USB Hub",
    "quantity": 90,
    "unitPrice": 5000
}

###SubmitInvoice Action - custom action to change invoice status to Submitted
POST http://localhost:4004/invoice/Invoices(30000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005)/InvoiceService.submitInvoice